A}} [[FC Girondins de Bordeaux|Bordeaux]], [[2005\u201306 Ligue 1#Top goalscorers|2005\u201306]], [[2006\u201307 Ligue 1#Top goalscorers|2006\u201307]] \u2013 {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]])\n*[[Jorge Cadete]] \u2013 '''1''' ([[1996\u201397 Scottish Premier Division#Top scorers|1996\u201397]] \u2013 {{flagicon|SCO}} [[Celtic F.C.|Celtic]])\n*[[Jos\u00e9 Andrade (Portuguese footballer)|Jos\u00e9 Gomes]] \u2013 '''1''' ([[2003\u201304 Luxembourg National Division|2003\u201304]] \u2013 {{flagicon|LUX}} [[CA Spora Luxembourg|Spora Luxembourg]])\n*[[Jorge Filipe Sa Silva]] \u2013 '''1''' ([[2003\u201304 Primera Divisi\u00f3|2003\u201304]] \u2013 {{flagicon|AND}} [[UE Sant Juli\u00e0|Sant Juli\u00e0]])\n*[[Bruninho (footballer, born 1986)|Bruninho]] \u2013 '''1''' ([[2012\u201313 Primera Divisi\u00f3|2012\u201313]] \u2013 {{flagicon|AND}} [[FC Lusitanos]])\n*[[Luis Miguel dos Reis]] \u2013 '''1''' ([[2013\u201314 Primera Divisi\u00f3|2013\u201314]] \u2013 {{flagicon|AND}} [[FC Lusitanos]])\n*[[Ariza Makukula]] \u2013 '''1''' ([[2009\u201310 S\u00fcper Lig#Top scorers|2009\u201310]] \u2013 {{flagicon|TUR}} [[Kayserispor]])\n*[[Marco Paix\u00e3o]] \u2013 '''1''' ([[2016\u201317 Ekstraklasa#Top goalscorers|2016\u201317]] \u2013 {{flagicon|POL}} [[Lechia Gda\u0144sk]])\n\n==Highest transfer fees==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin-right: 0;\"\n|- text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width:20px;\"| #\n! style=\"width:120px;\"| Name\n! style=\"width:180px;\"| From\n! style=\"width:170px;\"| To\n! style=\"width:110px;\"| Fee ([[Euro|\u20ac]] million)\n! style=\"width:120px;\"| Date\n! style=\"width:60px;\"| Source(s)\n|-\n|1\n|[[Jo\u00e3o F\u00e9lix]]\n||{{flagicon|Portugal}} [[S.L. Benfica|Benfica]]\n||{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Atl\u00e9tico Madrid]]\n|align=center|'''126'''\n|3 July 2019\n|align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.slbenfica.pt/pt-pt/agora/noticias/2019/07/03/futebol-benfica-comunicado-cmvm-joao-felix-atletico-de-madrid|language=p