                      = \n| timezone                        = [[East Africa Time|EAT]]\n| utc_offset                      = +3\n| timezone_DST                    = \n| utc_offset_DST                  = \n| coordinates                     = {{coord|9|45|24|N|47|31|38|E|region:SO-SA|display=inline,title}}\n| blank_name                      = \n| blank_info                      = \n}}\n'''Dararweyne''' is a small town in south-central [[Sanaag]] in Somaliland. the city is inhibited people from [[habarjeclo]], [[biciide]] especially [[faarax biciide (habarjeclo)]] and [[baho]] especially roobsuge faarax biciide<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maplandia.com/somalia/sanaag/ceerigaabo-erigavo/dararweyne/ |title=Dararweyne Map \u2014 Satellite Images of Dararweyne}}</ref> It is the second largest town in [[Erigavo District]] after the capital [[Erigavo]].<ref name=\"Map\">https://mapcarta.com/12469340</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://geographic.org/geographic_names/name.php?uni=-4560023&fid=5791&c=somalia Dararweyne]\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Sanaag]]\n\n{{Somaliland-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| official_name                   = Dararweyne\n| native_name                     = \n| other_name                      = \n| settlement_type                 = Town\n| imagesize                       = \n| image_flag                      = \n| flag_size                       = \n| image_seal                      = \n| seal_size                       = \n| nickname                        = \n| motto                           = \n| image_map                       = \n| mapsize                         = \n| map_caption                     = Location in Somaliland\n| pushpin_map                     = Somaliland\n| pushpin_label_position          = bottom\n| pushpin_mapsize                 = \n| subdivision_type                = Country\n| subdivision_name                = {{flag|Somaliland}}\n| subdivision_type1            